{
  "text": "The rest of the paper is organized as follows. In Section 2, we summarize the algorithmic routing proposed in Ref. [CITATION_1] which is the basis for our method. In Section 3 we overview our method and its details are explained in Section 4. Section 5 gives experimental results and Section 6 concludes the paper.",
  "citation_candidates": [
